definition: police classification/subdivision of policing activities (traffic, border guard, criminal etc)

sentences.english: Most people do not know how many kinds of police officers we have.
sentences.chinese: 一般人都不知道我們國家有多少警種。

sentences.english: Criminal police is a separate type of police.
sentences.chinese: 刑事警察是警察序列中的一個單獨警種。
